section.p:
Compile both projects by executing "mvn clean install" at the root folder of each project.
    Then copy myappweb.war into Tomcat "webapps" folder. After application will be deployed, open its SQLite database "ordering-web/myordering.sqlite" (I recomend H2 web-tool for it) and insert users:

insert into USTMC (USR, PWD, VER) values ('admin', 'admin', 1);
insert into USTMC (USR, PWD, VER) values ('user', 'user', 1);
insert into USRLTMC (USR, ROL, VER)  values ('admin', 'admin', 1);
insert into USRLTMC (USR, ROL, VER)  values ('user', 'user', 1);


* see web.xml JEE authentication part about roles and secure path.
After that you are able to login into "secure place" and make orders:


Lists, edit forms, entity pickers will be generated automatically.
